Author: El Farto
Body: Been using it for years, here is a future update feature request: make it possible to import multiple tokens.. that will earn you five stars

Author: Manoj Mishra
Subject: Amazing app
Body: This is really cool app. It helped me transferring token from previous device without going through IT team.

Author: Thanos Svigkos
Subject: Just one token
Body: 4stars for the moment because you cannot add more than one tokens at the same time. Unfortunately I had to change to another app due to this. If this is fixed it will well deserve the 5 stars.

Author: Simon Alphonse
Subject: Bad Looks
Body: Need transparent option for background and border.

Author: Paul Hedderly
Body: Do not even bother with the official RSA app. This one is brilliant.   The only improvement I would want is to be able to get tokens to tasker (via intents) so that I can push the token to my Pebble... Please Kevin - any chance?

Author: Phillip Simpson
Subject: Works great
Body: The official rsa secureid app started being flaky with the most recent update. My it department asked me to reinstall and sent me a qr code. I used that code to reactivate the rsa official app and this one. But I much prefer this one due to the widget.

Author: Shuvo Paul
Body: works good. But I am wondering if is there any way to restore old device id.

Author: Sherman Smith
Subject: Best RSA tool
Body: It's sad that the official RSA app doesn't work,this one works like a charm on all my Android devices. Save your stid file in Dropbox or your cloud storage and you'll be able to easily move from one device to another. As I said before, don't bother with the "official" RSA app. Thus app should be paid, but it's not.

Author: Arthur Blakely
Body: Like it so far would love it and 5 star if it gave android wear support!

Subject: Real time ....
Body: Future time and I see

Author: Martin Geisler
Body: For people who use their RSA token frequently, this is a real time saver! This app comes with a widget for quick access to the token — the original RSA SecurID app has no such thing.

Author: Akshay Paul
Subject: Great replacement
Body: No need for RSA token conversion. stdid file will be taken up. Plus u get a widget. Truly amazing.

Body: It is awesome app

Body: Better than RSA app!

Body: Better than original RSA SecuID app. Able to import directly from folder. Thanks pal!

Body: very good

Body: Simple to use....

Author: Gurpreet Grover
Subject: Great alternative for RSA Soft token
Body: .sdtid file can be imported in this unlike the original rsa app for android. Thanks for this utility, it helps alot.

Author: Kumar Ganapathy
Body: Works like a charm!!!!

Author: Michael Hopper
Subject: Works great!
Body: Finally a replacement for the long non-working official RSA token app!

Author: Terry Seiple
Subject: Great RSA Replacement for 4.4.4 OS
Body: I tried to get the RSA native client working but it wouldn't import from either QR code or URL. I added this app and moved my RSA .SDTID file to my Samsung Galaxy S5 and was able to install and configure my device and was logged in with my software token in less than 30 seconds. Sure beats the heck out of downloading all the JAR files and nonsense that one has to do with the native RSA conversion application. GREAT JOB!!!

Author: Dale Kirkley
Subject: Great app, but.....
Body: Works well, love that you can have your code as a widget, but I would really like support for multiple tokens, like the official RSA app. It's a free app, with no intrusive adverts, so I certainly don't feel entitled to anything, just putting it out there. Thanks again to the dev for all his hard work.

Author: Gavin Meerwald
Subject: Another great app
Body: Works well. Shame it wants to download Barcode Scanner when I already have QR Reader installed.

Subject: Excelente
Body: Funciono muy bien.

Author: John Zabroski
Body: Sweet app
